snippet.title: FIFA 13 Wii U Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hey football fans! Check out some FIFA 13 gameplay footage from the Wii U version as I picked it up very, very cheap in Argos a good while back. If you like this video, make sure to hit the thumbs up button and if you haven't already, do hit the fat red subscribe button. And as always, STAAAAY FRESH! #FIFA13 #FIFA #Football #Soccer #WiiU #Nintendo #NintendoImpactGaming #FIFASoccer13 #ManchesterUnited

Channel Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-MbkK99syg4

I do loads of stuff on the channel from gameplay videos, unboxings, podcast and a whole lot more. If you are interested in being part of an episode or want to say hey and get a shout out, just say hey in one of my videos. Thanks for checking out the channel and make sure to Subscribe, Like, Comment and Share as I am truly grateful! lol And please follow us on our other Social Network sites. Thanks! :)
